@Loopifyyy The main issue with blockchain games right now, isn't the tokenomics, it's ... the lack of fun. A large majority of the games out there are plain bad. 
Trying to convince normie gamers to come over to Web 3 is ludicrous if the game experience is that of a half-baked game.

There can never be enough art in the world.
So go put yours out there. The world needs it.
